sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant MMAPI as ModelMesh gRPC API<br/>8033/TCP TLS+mTLS
    participant Router as Routing / LRU Cache
    participant Runtime as Model Runtime<br/>8085/TCP or UDS<br/>plaintext
    participant Litelinks as Litelinks RPC<br/>8080/TCP Thrift
    participant RemoteMM as Remote ModelMesh Pod
    participant RemoteRT as Remote Model Runtime
    participant etcd as etcd Cluster<br/>2379/TCP TLS
    participant Storage as Model Storage<br/>(S3/PVC)

    rect rgb(230, 245, 255)
        Note over Client,Runtime: Flow 1: Model Inference Request (Local Cache Hit)
        Client->>MMAPI: gRPC inference RPC<br/>TLS + mTLS (optional)
        MMAPI->>Router: Route request by model ID
        Router->>Router: Check local LRU cache
        Router->>Runtime: Forward inference<br/>gRPC 8085/TCP plaintext
        Runtime-->>Router: Prediction result
        Router-->>MMAPI: Response
        MMAPI-->>Client: gRPC response
    end

    rect rgb(255, 240, 230)
        Note over Client,RemoteRT: Flow 1b: Model Inference Request (Cache Miss - Remote Forward)
        Client->>MMAPI: gRPC inference RPC<br/>TLS + mTLS (optional)
        MMAPI->>Router: Route request by model ID
        Router->>Router: Model not loaded locally
        Router->>Litelinks: Forward to instance with model<br/>Thrift 8080/TCP TLS (optional)
        Litelinks->>RemoteMM: Inter-pod invocation
        RemoteMM->>RemoteRT: Forward inference<br/>gRPC 8085/TCP plaintext
        RemoteRT-->>RemoteMM: Prediction result
        RemoteMM-->>Litelinks: Response
        Litelinks-->>Router: Response
        Router-->>MMAPI: Response
        MMAPI-->>Client: gRPC response
    end

    rect rgb(230, 255, 230)
        Note over Client,Storage: Flow 2: Model Registration and Loading
        Client->>MMAPI: registerModel RPC<br/>TLS + mTLS (optional)
        MMAPI->>Router: Register model
        Router->>etcd: Store model record<br/>gRPC 2379/TCP TLS
        etcd-->>Router: Confirmed
        Router->>Router: Select instance for loading<br/>(capacity-based placement)
        Router->>Runtime: loadModel RPC<br/>gRPC 8085/TCP plaintext
        Runtime->>Storage: Download model artifacts<br/>HTTPS/varies
        Storage-->>Runtime: Model data
        Runtime-->>Router: Model loaded (size reported)
        Router->>etcd: Update model state → LOADED
        Router-->>MMAPI: Registration response
        MMAPI-->>Client: Model registered + loaded
    end

    rect rgb(255, 230, 230)
        Note over MMAPI,etcd: Flow 3: Graceful Shutdown
        Note right of MMAPI: Kubernetes sends SIGTERM
        MMAPI->>Router: Begin graceful shutdown
        Router->>etcd: Deregister instance<br/>gRPC 2379/TCP TLS
        Router->>Litelinks: Trigger model loading on other instances<br/>Thrift 8080/TCP
        Litelinks->>RemoteMM: Propagate models
        RemoteMM->>RemoteRT: loadModel for migrated models
        Note right of MMAPI: PreStop server (8090) blocks<br/>runtime container until<br/>ModelMesh exits
    end
